The Plan For Procedural Generation Of Large Planets.

Level of Detail
  Parts of the planet which are closer to the player
    will have more vertices
Noise
  Basic fractal gradient noise
  Mountain peaks
Biomes
  Multiple climates on one planet
Sea level
  Is there any kind of ocean?
  Is it molten rock or metal?
  Is it water?
Temperature
  Hot planets use different textures than cold planets
Atmosphere
  Is it breathable?
  What color is it?
  How thick is it?
